---
title: North African-Inspired Falafel, Chicken and Couscous with Blistered Veggies and Spicy Mayo Sauce
description: Fresh, vibrant and colourful; this dish is inspired by the flavours of the Moroccan souq! With crunchy falafel, savoury chicken, fresh lemony couscous, sweet peppers and a zippy harissa spice drizzle, tonight's dinner is sure to become a new fam fave!
